ormal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去屯門同 立法會 我明 我認同<br />\n<br />\n76屯門令 更多當地 小理政治民眾 近距離見識黑警同 親中媒體 表現<br />\n<br />\n71立法會 令政府真正理解事件影響<br />\n<br />\n但 當政府一定唔會回應 <br />\n<br />\n而 選舉就到 <br />\n點解選街頭 而唔係選票<br />\n<br />\n黑材料都夠多啦 夠講 幾個鐘<br />\n減少人被補 全力打輿論戰<br />\n有咩問題？<br />\n最慘每次出去 都只係增加被補人士 你地心舒服咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9288f8331bbc25d19b62165868f085020635fe3f","tid":1294633,"uid":81071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2e8b473899c9dd0216ed9aabc5a5cc8b4bacf35","tid":1294633,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T22:58:52.000Z","msg":"起義"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T23:22:20.000Z","msg":"如果大眾未由 理解 轉向行動前 <br />\n點行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個個得過睇字 同尖叫"},{"pid":"7cada93ec0b82a8126663b4f60b5a3ffdbe7c6e0","tid":1294633,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9288f8331bbc25d19b62165868f085020635fe3f","tid":1294633,"uid":81071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2e8b473899c9dd0216ed9aabc5a5cc8b4bacf35","tid":1294633,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T22:58:52.000Z","msg":"起義"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T23:22:20.000Z","msg":"如果大眾未由 理解 轉向行動前 <br />\n點行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個個得過睇字 同尖叫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T23:23:43.000Z","msg":"Sor我唔岩<br />\n咁都係自殺啦"},{"pid":"19791843e48e283cf36ca5a6d580657d6840a77a","tid":1294633,"uid":248975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T23:25:53.000Z","msg":"我都想知佢地諗咩<br />\nbe water <br />\n浪費警察精神仲好啦<br />\n你諗下佢地次次出去都係比人屌<br />\n份工幾惡做